dev.jeka.core.api.depmanagement.artifact

Class JkStandardFileArtifactProducer<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • dev.jeka.core.api.depmanagement.artifact.JkStandardFileArtifactProducer<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JkArtifactLocator, JkArtifactProducer

    public class JkStandardFileArtifactProducer<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements JkArtifactProducer
    This JkArtifactProducer produces artifacts files at a standardized path determined by a provided function (outputPath, artifactId) -> path.

    This function is supposed to be supplied by the caller. To add artifacts to produce, caller has to provide a Consumer generating the artifact file at the given path.
